### REQUIRES AUTHENTICATION FIRST

### GET all authors
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/api/v1/authors
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### GET specific author
GET {{host}}:{{port}}/api/v1/authors/d0deaac3-6ef8-43c2-b53b-45480a406f26
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### POST create first author
POST {{host}}:{{port}}/api/v1/authors
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

